Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:12.86,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your High School National Ogura Hundred \NPoets Karuta Team champions:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:15.37,Chiha-main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa High School from Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:22.25,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:33.66,yuushou,,0000,0000,0000,,Champions\N\N{\fs18}1st: Fujisaki High School\N2nd: Fujisaki High School\N3rd: Fujisaki High School\N4th: Fujisaki High School\N5th: Fujisaki High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.81,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.39,go-on,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.33,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy.  Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.29,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:04.79,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,to win the team High \NSchool Championship...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.83,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We finally have new members...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.39,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:12.44,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to becoming Queen, becoming \Nthe strongest woman in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:15.22,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,it's much harder for us to \Nbecome best in Japan together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:17.22,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a boatsman adrift...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:58.10,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:01.11,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,800)}Episode 20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:01.11,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,800)}The\N fall\N paddy\N shacks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.18,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody have everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.84,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.43,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the trophy and other \Nawards sent back to the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.49,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so place everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.85,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to write out an invoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.84,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there in all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.88,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Ayase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:16.75,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is there a hospital still open nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.37,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.93,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's swollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.43,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say something sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.54,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I know of an emergency clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.79,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,We went there last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.90,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.67,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-san, should we get you \Nlooked at too, just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.96,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The swelling's gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.17,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.03,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun, can you take over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.57,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.17,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Will Chihaya-chan be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.16,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The individual tournament is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.82,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start packing the awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.44,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Should we put the medals inside, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.68,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.27,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need something \Nto serve as a cushion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.73,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,How about a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.05,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.01,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.05,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.18,sake,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Famous \NSake Manju
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.80,sake2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Fukui's famous sake manju...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.80,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, are you walking to the station, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.42,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,No, my uncle's coming in \Nhis car to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.07,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Hokuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:25.12,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!  Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.95,placement,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Third Place\NTokyo    Hokuo Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.78,Chiha-main-top,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,We're sprinting to the station, wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.55,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Boys' schools are full of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:30.32,placement,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fourth Place\NHyogo Prefecture   First Akashi Girls' High School
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.30,Chiha-main-top,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dying for a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.62,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call for a taxi, Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.74,Chiha-main-top,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.58,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We need to save our energy for the \Nindividual tournament tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.51,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:40.46,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya-san, Mashima-senpai, and \NAyase-senpai are childhood friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.30,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.19,Chiha-main-top,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.41,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,No way!  What kind of balance is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.77,Chiha-main-top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm childhood friends \Nwith Retro from Hokuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.47,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a love triangle in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.47,childhood,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.47,childhood,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)\an6}Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.93,Chiha-main-top,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.49,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Is your school co-ed, Wataya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.81,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's your type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.10,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:57.15,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,But!  But!  This is very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.15,Chiha-overlap,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Show some restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.66,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,But!  But!  But!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.79,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We're going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:01.40,Chiha-overlap,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel!  I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.79,Chiha-overlap,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.40,Chiha-main-top,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,What's for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.51,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know!  I wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:04.38,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.02,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,That girl also plays karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.53,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She's a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:10.72,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya worked hard to recruit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.50,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:16.71,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Team...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.21,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:26.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,the only team for me is the one \NI had with you and Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:39.07,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I sound pretty creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.94,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since I was \Nlooking up at the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.17,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.69,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,On a different subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:49.32,college,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.75,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning on going to college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.32,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which college?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.58,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Any place I can get a scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.60,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win the individual tournament tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.17,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,and go to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:03.94,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.91,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.17,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,coming to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:12.17,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's my uncle's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.74,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.64,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.43,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:22.31,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya wants to be on \Na team with you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.86,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:27.86,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.11,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.87,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.11,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.79,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!  What do you mean, Doctor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.34,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like \Nany bones were broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.74,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,but there appears to be a chip fracture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.44,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Chip fracture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:05.01,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,But a fracture would hurt more,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.03,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,and the swelling isn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.59,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write up a referral,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.57,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should go to a bigger \Nhospital for a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.90,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.23,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,She has a competitive \Nkaruta tournament tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.33,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Can she participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.85,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:23.08,gotit,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Wow, you're good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:23.08,gotit,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)\an8}Got it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:21.06,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean this, it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.08,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.61,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,She should refrain from \Nany intense activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.53,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,The bone has been weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.16,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be painful if you hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.22,Chiha-main,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,I would recommend that you give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.10,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.15,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.56,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you about to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:47.34,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.99,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.99,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about Ayase-san later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.71,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ms. Miyauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:55.49,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk to the inn staff, \Nthey'll serve dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.48,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:58.41,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.00,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Go take your bath, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.75,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Senpai.
