Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.31,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She moved faster than sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.82,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of birds...
