Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.38,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,One win for Pizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:31.21,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oe-senpai held on to win!  Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:33.63,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Two wins for Mizusawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.44,Chiha-flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.52,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent has "The sight of Mount,"
