Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:38.79,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I sigh and lament how the one \NI love does not feel the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:39.72,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.66,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.73,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.24,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Her reflexes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:45.66,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Her sense...
