Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.00,Chiha-flashback,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.90,Chiha-flashback,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.53,Chiha-flashback,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Win, Rion!
