Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.51,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.97,Chiha-flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Two wins for Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.35,Chiha-flashback,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusawa's down 0 to 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.60,Chiha-flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisaki's got this in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.88,Chiha-flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.35,Chiha-flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it a five-peat for Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.44,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Three wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.73,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting three wins, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.06,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:28.70,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's down to luck-of-the-draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:31.77,Chiha-flashback,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,In both games...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.51,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:39.32,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if my card is never \Nread in a luck-of-the-draw again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.82,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.19,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Just today...
