Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.89,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.76,Chiha-flashback,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You've got tatami marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:23.97,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
