Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.75,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.86,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You should forfeit, Ayase-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.34,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt even more if you hit it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.85,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.71,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
