Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.21,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.88,congrats,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations {\3c&H60605E&}Winners
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.96,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.35,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna wear this and play.
