Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.98,Chiha-internal,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.23,C,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Class C
