Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:01.56,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I expect this to give the \Nkaruta world a jolt, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:06.40,Chiha-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,No, in the team tournament, players \Nrely on strength to take cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:09.06,snotty,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an3}All Japan Karuta Association Chairman\NMashita Yoshiaki, grade 10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.53,Chiha-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,The matches are very messy to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.70,Chiha-main,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,However, in the individual tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:16.97,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we can expect battles of wit and strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.45,Bsuper,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Super Class A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.19,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt if you hit something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna play like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll use my left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:38.85,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can with my left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.48,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.43,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We're all playing to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.41,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The individual tournament \Nis about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.74,B2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(300,1)}Class A
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.05,writing,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,300)}Ayase Chihaya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:00.79,writing,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}Yuube Keiko
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.30,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.89,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,She's aggressive enough to blow you \Naway, even using your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.54,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to \Ndo with your left hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.59,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But!  But, but, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:23.47,unknown,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:23.47,stare,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.10,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the Queen so interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.73,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The first round should be a cinch for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.74,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,They should just seed her, for our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.48,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,How did she lose all that weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:27.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because they stopped \Nselling Snowmaru daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.73,stare,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}You know the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.98,writing,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.69,writing,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kawauchi Shoji
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.69,rainbow,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,1)}Wait, \NI'm\N playing \Nhim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.19,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I lucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.62,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing I didn't get paired \Nagainst Arata in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.27,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I would've had a taste of how \Nmuch stronger you've gotten
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.00,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,over the past few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.71,Chiha-internal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.51,Chiha-internal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.56,Chiha-internal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them admit that the team \Ntournament is nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.83,Chiha-internal,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.64,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen looked so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.87,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a cooling scarf around her neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:14.29,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.68,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will the players please step inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.51,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,The first round will soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.66,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Class A will be on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.02,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will the players please step inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:30.29,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.29,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.43,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.17,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.56,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata and I are standing \Non the same tatami floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.86,Chiha-main,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day...  \NToday is the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:58.25,Chiha-main,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day I win it all \Nand start the Legend of Retro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.74,asleep,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Kinashi Hiro's Road to Master Project\N{\c&H2713CE&}Classified
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.74,loveretro,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Retro
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.36,Chiha-main,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.46,Chiha-main,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.34,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Retro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.00,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:11.76,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is he burned out from \Nthe team tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.95,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:18.13,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like him, but that \Nmeans my greatest rival is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.96,Chiha-internal,Retro,0000,0000,0000,,My victory is assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.53,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The two first-years in Class D\Nare in a separate hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:35.66,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-kun and Oe-san in \NClass C are in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.04,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashima-kun will be playing the Class B\N first round on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.30,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,On the second floor is Class A, \NNishida-kun and Ayase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.36,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell this is the \Nnational tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.58,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The parents are here \Nto support the players.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.58,arata,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's dad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:49.58,arata2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Arata's mom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:58.92,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.80,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:16.10,Chiha-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the first round of \Nthe Class A individual tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.08,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.27,Chiha-main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:29.58,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:40.54,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:50.98,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring, now the flower blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.57,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gust of wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.57,Chiha-main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.69,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.97,Chiha-internal,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Not until I get to play Megumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:05.31,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...fall leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.02,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of birds crossing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.79,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.94,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:23.66,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but my body, my left hand won't...
